com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class ExtendedNodeLabelCandidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.LabelCandidate
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.NodeLabelCandidate
        • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ExtendedNodeLabelCandidate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPlaneObject

    public class ExtendedNodeLabelCandidate
extends NodeLabelCandidate
    A NodeLabelCandidate that provides a candidate descriptor.

    This class is used by LayoutExecutor and LayoutGraphAdapter to convert an IGraph into a corresponding Graph. Unless that conversion needs to be customized, or aforementioned classes cannot be used, this class usually doesn't need to be used explicitly.
